rue">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/housing-showers-electricity-these-are-the-outposts-the-idf-is-building-in-central-gaza/0000018e-f1da-dbb3-a3bf-f5df02120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 195 天：哈马斯官员称该组织并未放弃停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-195-hamas-official-says-group-hasnt-abandoned-truce-talks/0000018e-f21e-d240-a19f-f61fb9380001</link><description>伊朗高级指挥官：在以色列威胁报复的情况下，德黑兰可能会审查其“核学说” 美国高级官员告诉美国广播公司新闻，以色列在逾越节之前不太可能对伊朗进行报复 美国和以色列官员举行虚拟会议，讨论以色列在叙利亚开展地面行动的计划拉法 ■ 哈马斯高级官员表示，该组织尚未放弃停火谈判 ■ 卡塔尔“重新评估”作为调解人的角色 ■ 战争结束 195 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:58:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-195-hamas-official-says-group-hasnt-abandoned-truce-talks/0000018e-f21e-d240-a19f-f61fb9380001</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方以涉嫌煽动恐怖罪逮捕巴勒斯坦学者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/police-probe-palestinian-scholar-doubting-oct-7-sexual-violence-on-suspicion-of-incitement/0000018e-f1a4-daad-a3de-ffbf42e40000</link><description>Nadera Shalhoub-Kevorkian 教授被带到耶路撒冷附近的警察局接受调查。她的律师表示，这是一次非法逮捕，其目的是恐吓以色列学院中的任何批评声音。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:20:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/police-probe-palestinian-scholar-doubting-oct-7-sexual-violence-on-suspicion-of-incitement/0000018e-f1a4-daad-a3de-ffbf42e40000</guid></item><item><title>15名证人，三份供词，裸体尸体模型。 10月7日哈马斯强奸的所有证据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/witnesses-confessions-naked-dead-bodies-all-the-evidence-of-hamas-rape-on-oct-7/0000018e-f114-d92e-abfe-f77f7e3f0000</link><description>哈马斯 10 月 7 日的强奸行为已成为大屠杀中最具争议的话题之一。每一个出现的证词和细节都在以色列支持者和反对者之间的冲突中被武器化。现在，根据与数十位消息人士的对话，《国土报》的一项调查勾画出了哈马斯实施性犯罪的证据，以及缺失的证据。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 16:12:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/witnesses-confessions-naked-dead-bodies-all-the-evidence-of-hamas-rape-on-oct-7/0000018e-f114-d92e-abfe-f77f7e3f0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔是加沙战争解决方案的一部分，而不是问题的一部分</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/qatar-is-part-of-the-solution-to-gaza-war-not-the-problem/0000018e-f0c4-daad-a3de-fefff8c90000</link><description>美国议员发起的三起独立袭击事件似乎是协调一致的，他们指责卡塔尔在人质谈判和加沙临时停火方面缺乏进展。但这是一种明显不公平的评估，即使对本杰明·内塔尼亚胡来说这是一个方便的评估</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 15:41:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/qatar-is-part-of-the-solution-to-gaza-war-not-the-problem/0000018e-f0c4-daad-a3de-fefff8c90000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦摄影师在加沙拍摄的令人心酸的照片赢得了年度世界新闻照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/palestinian-photographer-wins-world-press-photo-of-the-year-with-poignant-shot-from-gaza/0000018e-f17d-d240-a19f-f57f28550000</link><description>路透社摄影师穆罕默德·塞勒姆 (Mohammed Salem) 凭借在汗尤尼斯 (Khan Yunis) 拍摄的失落场景获得年度世界新闻摄影奖，照片中 36 岁的伊纳斯·阿布·玛马尔 (Inas Abu Maamar) 抱着她五岁的侄女，她的侄女与她的母亲和妹妹一起被杀在以色列的一次袭击中</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:35:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/palestinian-photographer-wins-world-press-photo-of-the-year-with-poignant-shot-from-gaza/0000018e-f17d-d240-a19f-f57f28550000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室主任在总理审判中向国家证人提供带薪假期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-chief-offers-witness-in-pm-trial-paid-vacation-ahead-of-her-testimony/0000018e-f0ec-dc56-a9cf-f9ffc2310000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡曾试图罢免的总理办公室的一名法律顾问将在几周内就涉及滥用国家资金在内塔尼亚胡官邸提供餐饮服务的案件中作证。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 12:26:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-chief-offers-witness-in-pm-trial-paid-vacation-ahead-of-her-testimony/0000018e-f0ec-dc56-a9cf-f9ffc2310000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列来说，10 月 7 日是一场永远战争的开始。对于经济来说，这是否预示着永远的衰退？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/for-israel-october-7-marked-the-beginning-of-a-forever-war/0000018e-f10a-daad-a3de-ff3b6f320000</link><description>“全面胜利”是不可能的，战斗也没有结束的希望。但永久的战争将付出可怕的经济代价</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 12:05:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/for-israel-october-7-marked-the-beginning-of-a-forever-war/0000018e-f10a-daad-a3de-ff3b6f320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长正式要求联合国向加沙的以色列人质运送葡萄酒和无酵饼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/israel-minister-officially-asks-un-to-deliver-wine-matza-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018e-f0d9-d92e-abfe-f7ff5b9a0000</link><description>耶路撒冷事务部长梅厄·波鲁什在致联合国中东和平进程特别协调员的信中用希伯来语写道，除非获释，葡萄酒和无酵饼可以振奋以色列人质的精神</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:37:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/israel-minister-officially-asks-un-to-deliver-wine-matza-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018e-f0d9-d92e-abfe-f7ff5b9a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院将审理针对将警察局长隶属于本-格维尔的拟议法律的上诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-hear-appeal-against-proposal-to-subordinate-police-chief-to-ben-gvir/0000018e-f0ad-de39-a79e-fbaf7f0a0000</link><description>以色列高等法院将听取针对国家安全部长提议的以色列警察条例修正案的请愿书，该修正案将允许极右翼部长制定战略并干预调查</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:13:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-hear-appeal-against-proposal-to-subordinate-police-chief-to-ben-gvir/0000018e-f0ad-de39-a79e-fbaf7f0a0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么当定居者杀害巴勒斯坦人时以色列人不退缩</