 isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/hope-for-the-wars-end-spread-in-gaza-after-irans-attack-it-dissipated-quickly/0000018e-f033-d240-a19f-f43395680000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁表示没有义务向以色列国防军招募犹太学生或停止资助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-says-no-obligation-to-draft-yeshiva-students-to-idf-or-halt-their-funding/0000018e-f000-dbb3-a3bf-f5cd55cc0000</link><description>内阁的立场不利于司法部长，预计将在高等法院就此问题提出请愿书时要求一名独立律师。司法部长上周拒绝了这一请求，声称政府尚未就此事表明立场</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 07:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-says-no-obligation-to-draft-yeshiva-students-to-idf-or-halt-their-funding/0000018e-f000-dbb3-a3bf-f5cd55cc0000</guid></item><item><title>卫星图像显示伊朗弹道导弹袭击以色列空军基地造成的破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/satellite-image-shows-damage-from-iranian-ballistic-missile-strike-on-israeli-air-base/0000018e-ecba-daad-a3de-eebbd9190000</link><description>照片显示内瓦蒂姆空军基地 C-130 运输机附近滑行道受损，伊朗连夜袭击以色列，该基地遭到四枚弹道导弹袭击</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 03:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/satellite-image-shows-damage-from-iranian-ballistic-missile-strike-on-israeli-air-base/0000018e-ecba-daad-a3de-eebbd9190000</guid></item><item><title>人身威胁和骚扰：伊朗升级针对以色列人的心理战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/personal-threats-and-harassment-iran-escalates-psychological-warfare-against-israel/0000018e-ecc8-dbb3-a3bf-fdcdb1840000</link><description>在政府数据库泄露重要信息、向以色列人质家属发送模拟葬礼花圈以及记者受到威胁后，数十名前公务员收到了来自海外的骚扰电话。 “这是伊朗持续不断的骚扰、制造混乱和分裂社会的行为。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 03:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/personal-threats-and-harassment-iran-escalates-psychological-warfare-against-israel/0000018e-ecc8-dbb3-a3bf-fdcdb1840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和美国高级官员将就拉法行动进行虚拟会面；伊朗威胁要“审查”核武器学说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-live/five-idf-reservists-in-serious-condition-following-rocket-drone-strike-on-northern-israel/0000018e-eecd-daad-a3de-eeff299e0000</link><description>美国对伊朗无人机计划、钢铁、汽车行业实施新制裁 ■ 报告：以色列在逾越节之前不太可能对伊朗实施打击 ■ 美国国务院：美国将否决巴勒斯坦加入联合国的请求 ■ 哈马斯官员称人质协议/停火谈判尚未陷入僵局</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 01:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-live/five-idf-reservists-in-serious-condition-following-rocket-drone-strike-on-northern-israel/0000018e-eecd-daad-a3de-eeff299e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>